transformer	- main

downsample - resample array to bigger pixels
upsample - restore downsampled-array to original pixels
shift2d  - rigid-body 2D shift (by ndx, ndy)
gauss    - 2D Gaussian filter
display  - display 4 images

grad2d   - compute 2D gradient (x and y components returned separately as gx, gy)
warp2d   - 2D warp based upon gradients and difference

